title._content: Naine külakiigel / A woman on a swing

description._content: Naine külakiigel. Kiikumine on olnud kogu Eestis üks põlisemaid meelelahutusviise, kiigud olid igas külas ja kõrtsi juures, kohati taluõueski. Kiikumisel oli ka maagiline tähendus – seda seostati viljakuse ja aastaaegade vaheldumisega. - - - A woman on a swing. Swinging has been a traditional way of entertainment all over Estonia, there were swings in every village and by every tavern, sometimes even on farmyards. Swinging had also a magical meaning – it was associated with fertility and the changing of the seasons. ca 1900 Viitekood / Reference code: EAA.1451.1.109.7.18 Kirje andmebaasis FOTIS / Description in the database FOTIS: www.ra.ee/fotis/index.php?type=2&id=9544
